```python
# An embedded image representing the next frame button icon in the animation editor UI.
NextFrame = PyEmbeddedImage(
    "iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABwAAAAcCAIAAAD9b0jDAAAAA3NCSVQICAjb4U/..."
)
```
